data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style house, where convenience and comfort blend seamlessly. Nestled just blocks away from schools, parks, and shopping, and boasting easy access to major highways, commuting to work will be a breeze! With 3 bedrooms already on one level, this lovely home offers plenty of space for your family. Plus, there's even more potential with the option to create a fourth and fifth bedroom on the lower level?all you need is an egress window. Step into the detached two-car garage, providing ample room for your vehicles and storage needs. You'll find several updates, including newer windows, a completely renovated bathroom, a fresh roof, modern appliances, and a brand-new hot water heater. The current owners have cherished the fantastic location and lovingly maintained the property. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to call this house your home. Book a tour today and experience the charm and potential this property has to offer. Your dream lifestyle awaits!
